---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Rachel Griffard-Smith"
  description="About Rachel Griffard-Smith — scientist, artist, and lover of dogs and the outdoors."
>
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Bio -->
    <section class="about-hero">
      <img
        src="https://github.com/rachelgriffard/digital-cv/assets/95938614/787b7baf-c4f6-48bc-9b11-18b10ea2bbe5"
        alt="Rachel Griffard-Smith"
        class="about-avatar"
      />
      <h1 class="about-name">Rachel Griffard-Smith</h1>
      <p class="about-role">Bioinformatician &middot; University of Kansas Medical Center</p>

      <div class="about-icons">
        <a href="mailto:rachelgriffard@gmail.com" aria-label="Email">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rachelgriffard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="LinkedIn">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z" fill="#0A66C2"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3330-695X" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="ORCID">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 256 256" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M256 128c0 70.7-57.3 128-128 128C57.3 256 0 198.7 0 128 0 57.3 57.3 0 128 0c70.7 0 128 57.3 128 128z" fill="#A6CE39"/><path d="M86.3 186.2H70.9V79.1h15.4v107.1zM108.9 79.1h41.6c39.6 0 57 28.3 57 53.6 0 27.5-21.5 53.6-56.8 53.6h-41.8V79.1zm15.4 93.3h24.5c34.9 0 42.9-26.5 42.9-39.7C191.7 111.2 178 93 152 93h-27.7v79.4zM88.7 56.8c0 5.5-4.5 10.1-10.1 10.1s-10.1-4.6-10.1-10.1c0-5.6 4.5-10.1 10.1-10.1s10.1 4.5 10.1 10.1z" fill="#fff"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/rachelgriffard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="GitHub">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577 0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729 1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236 1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176 0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405 1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405 2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22 0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286 0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12" fill="#181717"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="about-bio-text">
        <p>
          I'm a bioinformatician, artist, and nature lover. When I'm not decoding
          biology with code and stats, I'm capturing moments through photography,
          crafting collages, or bouldering. 
        </p>
        <p>
          I work at the University of Kansas Medical Center, where I prioritize reproducible science
          by building pipelines and packagesfor multi-omic data types and analyses
          and contribute to published research across immunology, microbiome, and genomics.
        </p>
        <p>
          I am most passionate about the democratization of data. I am committed to ensuring that good
          science is not lost in poor visualizations, inaccessible code, or choppy writing; I strive to 
          take complex findings in biological data and making them accessible to not only a broad audience
          of scientists, but also to those without domain experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Photos -->
    <section class="about-gallery-section">
      <h2 class="about-gallery-title">Life Outside the Lab</h2>
      <div class="about-gallery-divider"></div>

      <div class="about-photo-group">
        <h3 class="about-photo-label">My Dogs</h3>
        <div class="photo-grid">
          <img src="/images/penny.jpg" alt="Penny Lane" />
          <img src="/images/duchess.jpg" alt="Duchess" />
          <img src="/images/hobbes.jpg" alt="Hobbes" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-photo-row">
        <div class="about-photo-group">
          <h3 class="about-photo-label">Us</h3>
          <img src="/images/rachel-and-jack.JPG" alt="Rachel and Jack" class="about-photo-single" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-photo-group">
          <h3 class="about-photo-label">Rock Climbing</h3>
          <img src="/images/climbing.gif.gif" alt="Rachel rock climbing" class="about-photo-single" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
